        Handle the search of the similarities between entities, filtered by Node Triple Store and Class Name
        Specified by:
        findEntitiesLinksByNodeAndTripleStoreAndClass in interface EntitiesHandlerService
        Parameters:
        node - String. The Node name to filter
        tripleStore - . The Triple Store name to filter
        className - . The Class Name to filter
        searchInOtherNodes - boolean. If true, then a search will be made in other nodes to find links, in another case only look for similarities in the same node
        deltaDate - boolean. If true, then Similarities will only be searched for entities that have changed since the last search, otherwise it will be performed on all entities
        Returns:
        Set, with the Similarities results, in the form SimilarityResult
